data.description: Country Living at its FINEST!  Gorgeous Victorian beauty on 5 irrigated acres ensuring your peace and quiet. This custom home is packed full of surprises and luxuries not easily found in today's market. 4 or 5 bedrooms offer plenty of space with separate formal and informal gathering rooms, perfect for today's lifestyle. Large kitchen opens up to the family room & patio area and features upgraded appliances plus easy care surfaces. Outdoor spaces include both shady and sunny patios plus a classic gazebo!
